data.title: Mary, Mother Of Jesus
data.meta_description: OCD17_PriestsIndex - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is an alphabetical list of Catholic priests in the United States reported for this issue. It provides abbreviations for various religious orders and congregations that the priests belong to such as Franciscans, Jesuits, Dominicans, and more. The list then begins with individual priests' names and the abbreviations of their respective orders.
